Master Samon.

33
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:03,840
Is this really enough to stop the princess?

34
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,510
On this island,

35
00:03:05,510 --> 00:03:08,840
she won't be able to acquire the offerings she needs to use magic.

36
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:12,300
As such, the princess is no different than an ordinary girl.

37
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,740
So the princess...

38
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:17,800
Yes, she will perish on that island.

39
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:20,390
<i>That's Samon for you.</i>

40
00:03:20,390 --> 00:03:23,790
He probably put up a barrier to make the island invisible, too.

41
00:03:24,330 --> 00:03:27,360
I won't be able to seek help from outside.

42
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,460
Guess I'm stranded in the middle of nowhere.

43
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,280
Look here, Samon! You better watch your back!

44
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,150
I'm Kusaribe Hakaze,

45
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:38,890
the strongest mage ever born into our clan!

46
00:03:38,890 --> 00:03:41,960
I'll put an end to your ambitions—

47
