316
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:20,250
With that, I was able to communicate with the mage on an isolated island.

317
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:22,570
And then we made a deal.

318
00:19:22,570 --> 00:19:24,040
So that's who that was...

319
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:26,640
In exchange for my help,

320
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:31,040
I told her to use her magic to find Aika's killer.

321
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:35,440
Aika's murder made no sense.

322
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:37,150
Magic doesn't make sense, either.

323
00:19:37,150 --> 00:19:40,250
Maybe two wrongs do make a right.

324
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:43,220
I will kill Aika's murderer with my own hands.

325
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:46,180
<i>I believe it...</i>

326
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:48,070
<i>But...</i>

327
00:19:48,650 --> 00:19:49,670
By the way,

328
00:19:49,670 --> 00:19:53,130
