336
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:13,170
Oh, someone mentioned it.

337
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:15,390
<i>This is crazy...</i>

338
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,430
Look, Yoshino...

339
00:20:25,870 --> 00:20:30,040
That's a part of what we're trying to stop!

340
00:20:39,670 --> 00:20:41,650
Return, return, return, return.

341
