Return, return, return, return.
Return, divided fruit!

342
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:45,970
Greatest of all trees, which raises itself above all others...

343
00:20:45,970 --> 00:20:48,830
Greatest of all trees, which raises itself above all others...
Return, return, return, return, return.

344
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:51,080
Return, return, return, return, return.
