Beautiful, beautiful. Fruit, fruit. Beautiful...

346
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:13,880
What the...

347
00:21:14,660 --> 00:21:17,770
When did the whole world go insane, exactly?

348
00:21:17,770 --> 00:21:20,860
I don't care if this world crumbles to ashes.

349
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:22,860
However, Yoshino...

350
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:25,700
